  \ with him. we talk so much we talk shit we smoke together .  we both trying impress\
  \ the same girl . we ride on a same scutty . we do so many things together . his\
  \ farther lives in spain . as we grow up . we pass our scholl . now from the morning\
  \ till night we stay together with our frinds we enjoy a lot car rides many things\
  \ we do then one day  i get know that he is also planning to go abroad . then he\
  \ make her passport and apply for the visa then he tell me that he is going to Portugal\
  \ on 19 may . by birthday is on same day \nthat situation when he is going away\
  \ from me i m broked from inside but i am smiling that oky  bro go happy have  great\
  \ life enjoy there. and he go and  i still have pirture of her in mind when he is\
  \ going .\noky then i back to home \ni join collage then from that day my life is\
  \ totaly change i never think that one day he will go and leave me . \nhe is busy\
  \ in his life there\ni m busy here with my new life \nwe some time do video call\
  \ he show me the Portugal and tell me about their culture \nits beed more than 4\
  \ year he is in Portugal \nthen recently he came to delhi . the movement when i\
  \ saw him for me i dont have words to explan that movement nothing is changed i\
  \ fell like that is their only . i m so happy to so him but he here only for few\
  \ days . then now he go back \nand now again i fell so lonly . it is so difficult\
  \ for me when he first time go then . now all that repeats . but i m okay \n chill\
  \ \ni saw that you are giving opportunity to travel  to Portugal i am very thank\
